 /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/104904_5a3334ec7800b012c0bf53464a6ad23b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F104904_5a3334ec7800b012c0bf53464a6ad23b.png&h=c46cdcb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"見到個女人吐痰張圖，腦海即刻響起香港97嗰首背景音樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"我愛北京天安門<br />\n天安門上太陽升"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9416ead0b6b1bad42584fedbb2a0a532de60e26b","tid":832651,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"係支那區吐痰 洗唔洗罰1500？"},{"pid":"b5f7c4bb1bea352b1b5d758e020d7793f7ea09f6","tid":832651,"uid":10249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"嗚嗚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3842b7734e3c0592844eb584f140a6ea7025bd6f","tid":832651,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9416ead0b6b1bad42584fedbb2a0a532de60e26b","tid":832651,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"係支那區吐痰 洗唔洗罰1500？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我上網search吓蚑那法律其實有,不過佢哋根本都唔撚執行嘅</span></span><br />\n城市市容和環境衛生管理條例<br />\n<br />\n第三十四條　有下列行為之一者，城市人民政府市容環境衛生行政主管部門或者其委託的單位除責令其糾正違法行為、採取補救措施外，可以並處警告、罰款：<br />\n<br />\n﻿（一）隨地吐痰、便溺，亂扔果皮、紙屑和煙頭等廢棄物的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（二）在城市建築物、設施以及樹木上塗寫、刻畫或者未經批准張掛、張貼宣傳品等的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（三）在城市人民政府規定的街道的臨街建築物的陽台和窗外，堆放、吊掛有礙市容的物品的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（四）不按規定的時間、地點、方式，傾倒垃圾、糞便的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（五）不履行衛生責任區清掃保潔義務或者不按規定清運、處理垃圾和糞便的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（六）運輸液體、散裝貨物不作密封、包紮、覆蓋，造成泄漏、遺撒的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（七）臨街工地不設置護欄或者不作遮擋、停工場地不及時整理並作必要覆蓋或者竣工後不及時清理和平整場地，影響市容和環境衛生的。"},{"pid":"0ff4c17b8ed4a2aeb8935ae2c5b8b391709b1437","tid":832651,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffab8e35a10a7184f561afc188f097f9a7fe4a8","tid":832651,"uid":137921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那人沒有一個是文明的"},{"pid":"73ee18dac8fb4aa8388ff1989beb30af13ee757f","tid":832651,"uid":150775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"支那賤種幾時先可以滅絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2543260186a8c96aaf548ec4be9dd8b1cfab297b","tid":832651,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3842b7734e3c0592844eb584f140a6ea7025bd6f","tid":832651,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9416ead0b6b1bad42584fedbb2a0a532de60e26b","tid":832651,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"係支那區吐痰 洗唔洗罰1500？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我上網search吓蚑那法律其實有,不過佢哋根本都唔撚執行嘅</span></span><br />\n城市市容和環境衛生管理條例<br />\n<br />\n第三十四條　有下列行為之一者，城市人民政府市容環境衛生行政主管部門或者其委託的單位除責令其糾正違法行為、採取補救措施外，可以並處警告、罰款：<br />\n<br />\n﻿（一）隨地吐痰、便溺，亂扔果皮、紙屑和煙頭等廢棄物的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（二）在城市建築物、設施以及樹木上塗寫、刻畫或者未經批准張掛、張貼宣傳品等的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（三）在城市人民政府規定的街道的臨街建築物的陽台和窗外，堆放、吊掛有礙市容的物品的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（四）不按規定的時間、地點、方式，傾倒垃圾、糞便的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（五）不履行衛生責任區清掃保潔義務或者不按規定清運、處理垃圾和糞便的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（六）運輸液體、散裝貨物不作密封、包紮、覆蓋，造成泄漏、遺撒的；<br />\n<br />\n﻿（七）臨街工地不設置護欄或者不作遮擋、停工場地不及時整理並作必要覆蓋或者竣工後不及時清理和平整場地，影響市容和環境衛生的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"正喎 一人吐一啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbf416476318e7e334f8067bef68b97cf3f3614","tid":832651,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cee7fd413cd456ec8a9c2c29393fb6bd11d9869","tid":832651,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fbf416476318e7e334f8067bef68b97cf3f3614","tid":832651,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"係啊，有咩問題咁呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1181f322178ad4b0c9d757905e30015001b21446","tid":832651,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xASlCFGozYs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxASlCFGozYs&d=REILfn9PG8J42kYIDykZ0P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9eebe3cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xASlCFGozYs</a>"}]}